<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Service Request - {{orderTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            margin: -30px -30px 20px -30px;
        }
        .order-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }
        .client-info {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border: 1px solid #bbdefb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.4);
        }
        .cta-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            color: #28a745;
            border: 2px solid #28a745;
            padding: 13px 28px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 10px 10px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .info-item {
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .info-value {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            color: #0c5460;
        }
        .opportunity-highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3cd 0%, #ffeaa7 100%);
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #155724;
        }
        .steps {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .step-number {
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 15px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .info-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .cta-button, .cta-secondary {
                display: block;
                text-align: center;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üíº New Service Opportunity</h1>
            <p>A client is looking for your expertise!</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Hello {{vendorName}},</h2>
        
        <p>Great news! <strong>{{clientName}}</strong> has invited you to provide services for their project. This could be a perfect opportunity to showcase your skills and grow your business.</p>

        <div class="opportunity-highlight">
            <h3>üí∞ Potential Earnings</h3>
            <div class="amount">‚Ç¶{{orderAmount}}</div>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #856404;">Estimated project value</p>
        </div>

        <div class="order-details">
            <h3>üìã Project Details</h3>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Project Title</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{orderTitle}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Project ID</div>
                    <div class="info-value">#{{orderNumber}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Status</div>
                    <div class="info-value">
                        <span class="status-badge">{{orderStatus}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Category</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{orderCategory}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if orderDescription}}
            <div style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <div class="info-label">Project Description</div>
                <div class="info-value" style="background-color: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 3px solid #28a745;">
                    {{orderDescription}}
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if startDate}}
            <div class="info-grid" style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Preferred Start Date</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{startDate}}</div>
                </div>
                {{#if endDate}}
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Expected Completion</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{endDate}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if requirements}}
            <div style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <div class="info-label">Special Requirements</div>
                <div class="info-value">{{requirements}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        <div class="client-info">
            <h3>üë§ Client Information</h3>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Client Name</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{clientName}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Company</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{clientCompany}}</div>
                </div>
                {{#if clientLocation}}
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Location</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{clientLocation}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if clientRating}}
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="info-label">Client Rating</div>
                    <div class="info-value">‚≠ê {{clientRating}}/5.0</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="steps">
            <h3>üöÄ Next Steps</h3>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <div>
                    <strong>Review the project details</strong><br>
                    <small>Make sure the project aligns with your expertise and availability</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <div>
                    <strong>Submit your proposal</strong><br>
                    <small>Include your timeline, approach, and any questions you may have</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <div>
                    <strong>Negotiate terms</strong><br>
                    <small>Discuss project details, pricing, and deliverables with the client</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <div>
                    <strong>Start earning</strong><br>
                    <small>Begin work once both parties agree on the terms</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <h3>Interested in this opportunity?</h3>
            <p>Review the full project details and submit your proposal:</p>
            
            <a href="{{orderUrl}}" class="cta-button">View Project & Submit Proposal</a>
            <a href="{{declineUrl}}" class="cta-secondary">Decline Invitation</a>
        </div>

        <div class="security-notice">
            <strong>‚úÖ PayBud Protection:</strong> This project is protected by PayBud's secure payment system. You'll receive payment once milestones are completed and approved. <strong>Invitation expires in 7 days.</strong>
        </div>

        <h3>Why choose this opportunity?</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>üí≥ Secure payments:</strong> All transactions are protected by PayBud's escrow system</li>
            <li><strong>üìà Build your reputation:</strong> Complete successful projects to improve your vendor rating</li>
            <li><strong>ü§ù Direct communication:</strong> Work directly with the client through our platform</li>
            <li><strong>üìä Track progress:</strong> Use our project management tools to stay organized</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Need Support?</h3>
        <p>If you have questions about this opportunity or need assistance:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>üí¨ Message the client directly through the project page</li>
            <li>üìß PayBud Vendor Support: vendors@paybud.com</li>
            <li>üìö Vendor Resources: <a href="{{vendorHelpUrl}}">paybud.com/vendors/help</a></li>
            <li>üìû Call us: +234 (0) 123 456 7890</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We're excited to help you win this project and grow your business!</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The PayBud Vendor Success Team</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
                This invitation was sent to {{vendorEmail}} by {{clientName}}<br>
                Project posted on {{invitationDate}}
            </p>
            
            <p>¬© 2024 PayBud. All rights reserved.<br>
            <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe from vendor opportunities</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
